<p align="left"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">The teacher of each course will explain the grading system in class. <br />Based on a maximum score of 100, grades will be awarded as follows: <br />S (Excellent) 90 - 100 A (Very good) 80-90 B (Good) 70-80 C (Pass) 60-70 D (Fail) Below 60.</span></p></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">事前・事後学修等の指示及び履修にあたっての注意事項</div><div style="margin:10px"><p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Preview: Preparation of textbook and other learning materials (120 minutes)</span></p>
